elements.expression:
esdocs sort="timestamp,desc" index="kibana_sample_data_flights" fields="timestamp, DistanceMiles" count=1000  
| pointseries x="timestamp" y="sum(DistanceMiles)" size="sum(DistanceMiles)"
| plot defaultStyle={seriesStyle points="0" lines="0" color="#FFFFFF" bars="0" fill=10} xaxis=false yaxis=false
| render containerStyle={containerStyle backgroundColor="#9FB746" padding="10px"}

timelion query=".es(timefield=timestamp, index=kibana_sample_data_flights, metric='sum:DistanceMiles', offset=+3h).mvavg(3)" interval="10m" from=now+30d to="now+33d"
| pointseries x="@timestamp" y="value"
| plot defaultStyle={seriesStyle points="0" lines="4" color="#FFFFFF"} xaxis=false yaxis=false
| render containerStyle={containerStyle backgroundColor="#E59C55" padding="10px"}

essql 
  query="SELECT timestamp AS x, DistanceMiles AS y from kibana_sample_data_flights ORDER BY x DESC"
| pointseries x="x" y="sum(y)" 
| plot 
  defaultStyle={seriesStyle points="0" lines="0" fill=true color="#FFFFFF" bars=50000} xaxis=false yaxis=false 
  font={font family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size=14 align="left" color="#FFFFFF" weight="bold" underline=false italic=false}
| render containerStyle={containerStyle backgroundColor="#C2435F" padding="10px"}

essql 
  query="SELECT timestamp AS x, DistanceMiles AS y from kibana_sample_data_flights ORDER BY x DESC"
| pointseries x="x" y="sum(y)"
| plot 
  defaultStyle={seriesStyle points="0" lines="0" bars="0.5" fill=10 color="#FFFFFF"} xaxis=false yaxis=false 
  font={font size=14 family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" color="#000000" align="left"}
| render 
  containerStyle={containerStyle backgroundColor="#C2435F" padding="5px" border="5px solid rgba(255,255,255,0)"}

shape "square" fill="#444444" border="rgba(255,255,255,0)" borderWidth=0 maintainAspect=false
| render

timefilter from="now-1d" to="now"
| markdown "errors found
" 
  font={font family="Futura, Impact, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size=30 align="center" color="#FFFFFF" weight="normal" underline=false italic=false}
| render

markdown {filters| escount query="error"} 
  font={font family="Futura, Impact, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size=96 align="center" color="#FFFFFF" weight="normal" underline=false italic=false}

filters
| demodata
| markdown "# Thanks" 
  font={font family="'Open Sans', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" size=36 align="center" color="#FFFFFF" weight="normal" underline=false italic=false}
| render
